425
00:30:24,083 --> 00:30:25,151
Ini.

426
00:30:25,152 --> 00:30:26,192
Oh.

427
00:30:27,152 --> 00:30:28,162
Terima kasih.

428
00:30:41,603 --> 00:30:42,744
